channel.title: Cant loggin to my server. Everythings Online
channel.description:
I already portfowarded and changed all the IP addresses from local(127.0.0.1) to my no-ip. I even started hosting from dropbox. Everything loads and is online. The webclient loads, im able to make a server on rswebclients, and I can list my rsps on other websites like these. Status says its online and everything looks right but when i try loggin in to play, it says im unable to join, like it's offline. This happens to me and other people who try playing. It might have something to do with my IP, as i have looked into this before posting, and i hope someone can help me out.
---Ishh

item.description:
@joelandjacob wrote:

Ishh, The error your getting I think might be your client. You’ve changed the ip address to your no-ip… You have to connect to your server with your client ip set to 127.0.0.1 (localhost) and give other players the no-ip.
